OL,3,CPair murdered Yeovil neighbour after
OL,4,Crow over rubbish
OL,6,FTwo men have been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering their neighbour in Yeovil
OL,8,Ffollowing a row over rubbish.
OL,10,FMartin Carty and Mark Sothcott were
OL,11,Ffound guilty of killing their
OL,12,Fneighbour Frank Ingram at Carty's flat
OL,13,Fin Raglan Terrace in June.
OL,15,FBristol Crown Court previously heard
OL,16,Fhow it had taken the men more than 18
OL,17,Fhours for either of them to call the
OL,18,Femergency services, and when Carty did
OL,19,Fphone 999 he falsely claimed to have
OL,20,Fdiscovered Mr Ingram dead on his sofa.
