OL,3,CPair murdered Yeovil neighbour after
OL,4,Crow over rubbish
OL,6,FDuring a three-week trial, the jury
OL,7,Fwere told that on the afternoon of 22
OL,8,FJune, there had been an exchange of
OL,9,Fwords after Carty had left rubbish
OL,10,Fnear Mr Ingram's flat.
OL,12,FA CCTV recording was played in which
OL,13,F68-year-old Mr Ingram later described
OL,14,FCarty as an 'idiot' to another
OL,15,Findividual, stating he was going to
OL,16,Fcontact the housing association
OL,17,Fresponsible for the flats.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
