OL,3,CPair murdered Yeovil neighbour after
OL,4,Crow over rubbish
OL,6,FShortly before 11pm, an 'angry' Mr
OL,7,FIngram went up to Carty's flat with a
OL,8,Fhammer. Both Carty and Sothcott were
OL,9,Finside the home.
OL,11,FA fight broke out between the three
OL,12,Fmen and 68 year-old Mr Ingram was
OL,13,Fheadbutted and struck by the hammer.
OL,15,FCarty called the ambulance service at
OL,16,Fabout 6.40pm the following day to say
OL,17,Fhe had found Mr Ingram deceased. He
OL,18,Fclaimed Mr Ingram had been to his flat
OL,19,Fthe night before in an agitated state,
OL,20,Fand he had let him sleep on his couch.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
