OL,3,CPair murdered Yeovil neighbour after
OL,4,Crow over rubbish
OL,6,FEmergency services attended and found
OL,7,Fthat Mr Ingram's injuries were not
OL,8,Fconsistent with Carty's story and he
OL,9,Fwas subsequently arrested.
OL,11,FSothcott was arrested the following
OL,12,Fday following information from members
OL,13,Fof the public who heard comments he
OL,14,Fhad made leaving the flat on the night
OL,15,FMr Ingram was killed.
OL,17,FA jury unanimously found Carty and
OL,18,FSothcott, both 58, guilty of murder
OL,19,Fafter a three-week trial at Bristol
OL,20,FCrown Court.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
