OL,3,CPair murdered Yeovil neighbour after
OL,4,Crow over rubbish
OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer, DCI Mark
OL,7,FAlmond, said: "The medical evidence
OL,8,Fclearly demonstrated that a serious
OL,9,Fand sustained violent attack was
OL,10,Fcarried out against Frank Ingram. The
OL,11,Fseverity of the injuries caused shows
OL,12,Fthe true intent of their actions.
OL,14,F"They both knew they had at least
OL,15,Fseriously injured him, and most likely
OL,16,Fkilled him, and the fact neither of
OL,17,Fthem called the emergency services for
OL,18,Fmore than 18 hours is truly horrendous.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
