OL,6,F"Frank Ingram's family has received
OL,7,Fsupport from specially-trained
OL,8,Fofficers ever since the tragic events
OL,9,Fof 22 June and our thoughts remain
OL,10,Fwith them.
OL,12,F"While we welcome these verdicts and
OL,13,Fhope the family take comfort in the
OL,14,Ftruth being put before the courts, we
OL,15,Frecognise this cannot erase the pain
OL,16,Fthey continue to experience after such
OL,17,Fa devastating loss."
